OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTeacher pay 'very difficult
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchoice' - minister         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, How much to pay teachers is a "very    
OL,6, difficult choice", a minister has said,
OL,7, as strikes hit schools in England for  
OL,8, the second time this week.             
OL,10,FRobert Halfon said the government      
OL,11,Fwanted to be fair to teaching staff but
OL,12,Falso "fair to the taxpayer".           
OL,14,FMany schools are expected to be closed 
OL,15,For part-closed as National Education   
OL,16,FUnion (NEU) members strike over pay.   
OL,18,FThe union said whether strikes should  
OL,19,Fcontinue in the autumn term was "in the
OL,20,Fgovernment's hands".                   
